    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in truly good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for throughout its life. It runs smoothly and looks great, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience for its next owner. While it shows some light, expected signs of use, it remains a solid and stylish choice for anyone looking for a high-quality vehicle at a great price!",
