    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation without the premium price of a newer model. The exterior shows typical signs of age, including some fading paint on the roof and a few minor door dings from parking lots. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some wear, and all major electronics are functional, though the air conditioning takes a moment to get cold. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
