    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a balanced synthesis of performance and value. Every component has been vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for roadworthiness and cabin comfort. Secure a vehicle that promises reliability and sophisticated engineering without compromise.",
      "price": 34500.0,
